## Image Processing Project 4


## Overview
- label card rank and suit

# Usage
- run 'image_capture.py' script
- upload folder of test images or select webcam option
- if webcam option chosen, follow terminal instructions to take a snapshot 
- ensure card is in fram with black background and clear features

# Assumptions:
- good enough quality to discern card rank and suit
- black background


