## Requirements
- These programs were developed and tested with Python 3.9 and require the following third-party packages:

- opencv-python >= 4.5
- numpy >= 1.19
- matplotlib >= 3.3

## SOURCES
- Card image samples used to create masks: https://github.com/Xadeck/xCards